    <h1 data-i18n="article.affiliate.title">Affiliate Marketing for Beginners: Is It Still Worth It in 2026?</h1>
    <div class="article-meta">
      <span><i data-lucide="clock" class="icon-xs"></i> <span data-i18n="article.affiliate.readtime">15 min read</span></span>
